ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce de Cowansville et région ** Change Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE COWANSVILLE ET RÉGION, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of the district of the Chambre de commerce de Cowansville et région from Cowansville, Dunham, St-Armand, Frelighsburg et Brigham to Cowansville, Dunham, Frelighsburg, Saint-Armand, Brome, Bromont, Abercorn, Canton de Bedford, Bedford, Brigham, East-Farnham, Notre-Dame de Stanbridge, Pike River, Saint-Ignace de Stanbridge, Stanbridge-East, Stanbridge Station, and Sutton.
AttachmentsAttachment
